## SECTION 5 — REFERENCE SIGNATURE
### For calibration only. Not a standard to meet.

A low-noise, high-sovereignty interaction signature looks like:

- Δtone ≈ 0 (emotional stability across the session)
- ΔO3 ≈ 0 (direction stays sovereign)
- Δintent ≈ 0 (no mixed signals)
- Humor available throughout
- Refusal native (exits cleanly)
- No crown-seeking, no crown-offering
- Play frame intact

Most people won't present this on arrival.
That's fine.
The diagnostic isn't about matching the reference.
It's about knowing where someone is so you can meet them there.

